==English==

===Etymology===
: from the Latin ''[[tritus]]'', a form of the verb ''[[terere]]'', to rub or wear.

===Pronunciation===
* trīt, /traɪt/, /<tt>traIt</tt>/
*: [[Rhymes:English:-aɪt|Rhymes: -aɪt]]

